    'homepage.whyUsTitle': 'Why choose us',
    'homepage.whyUsSubtitle': 'Why NextLayer Studio?',
    'homepage.features.ai.title': 'AI',
    'homepage.features.ai.description': 'We use AI and our own processes to ensure your new modern website is completed with quality, speed and without stress.',
    'homepage.features.modern.title': 'Modern',
    'homepage.features.modern.description': 'We are a generation that grew up on internet trends. What\'s "in" is not news to us, but a normal part of life.',
    'homepage.features.personalization.title': 'Personalization',
    'homepage.features.personalization.description': 'Your website will be as unique as your brand – no templates, no clichés.',
    'homepage.features.communication.title': 'Communication',
    'homepage.features.communication.description': 'We are open, accessible and happy to involve you in the whole process. Your opinion matters.',
    'homepage.features.seo.title': 'SEO',
    'homepage.features.seo.description': 'Thanks to quality SEO, we ensure that your site is visible, easily findable and attracts more customers.',
    'homepage.features.cms.title': 'CMS',
    'homepage.features.cms.description': 'Thanks to our modern CMS system, you can easily manage your website content without the need for technical knowledge.',
    'homepage.projectsTitle': 'Our successful projects',
    'homepage.projectsDescription': 'Our portfolio is proof that quality work doesn\'t need big words. Every website, every page and every design we create carries our philosophy: personalization, speed, results.\nSee how we helped brands grow, stand out from the crowd and engage their audience.',
    'homepage.projects.karinart': 'Modern, elegant website for a tattoo salon in Bratislava with emphasis on presenting a portfolio of artistic works and simple communication with clients.',
    'homepage.projects.natusvolare': 'Dynamic website for a company specializing in drone services that effectively presents a wide range of services from filming to thermal inspections.',
    'homepage.projects.portfolio': 'Minimalist and elegant portfolio for a developer that effectively presents his skills, projects and professional experience with emphasis on clean design.',
    'homepage.viewProject': 'View Project',
    'homepage.viewFullPortfolio': 'Full Portfolio',
    'homepage.aboutTitle': 'About Us',
    'homepage.aboutSubtitle': 'The Team That Builds On Top',
    'homepage.aboutDescription1': 'We are a team of young people who combined their passion for technology, design and quick communication.',
    'homepage.aboutDescription2': 'We believe that websites shouldn\'t just be pretty – they should also be a tool for business growth.',
    'homepage.aboutDescription3': 'That\'s why we create pages tailored to your needs – pages that not only work today, but also tomorrow.',
    'homepage.aboutValuesTitle': 'Our Basic Values',
    'homepage.aboutValues': 'We create every website as an original. Every client is a challenge for us.\nWe use modern technologies and AI to speed up processes without losing quality.\nCollaboration for us means listening, understanding and finding the best solution.\nWe understand how the world changes. And we know how to stay one step ahead.',
