    // About Us page
    'about.title': 'What is NextLayer Studio',
    'about.subtitle': 'The Team That Builds On Top',
    'about.paragraph1': 'Next Layer Studio is a young, dynamic team of developers, designers and technology enthusiasts united by the desire to push the boundaries of what\'s possible and transform modern technologies into practical solutions. We design and program fast responsive websites and e-shops, build comprehensive web applications – from internal portals and booking systems to production line monitoring tools – and help companies save time by connecting these solutions to their processes, automating inventory, payroll or document approval.',
    'about.paragraph2': 'When you start working with us, we first listen carefully to your problem to understand the goals and daily tasks of your people. Based on this, we propose a solution in which we use only those technologies and features that will actually bring you benefit. During development, we continuously show the real version of the application, collect feedback and fine-tune details, until the result perfectly fits your requirements. However, work doesn\'t end with deployment: we provide support, maintenance and are ready to further develop the project when your business grows.',
    'about.paragraph3': 'We are not afraid of innovation, we follow current trends and implement them wherever they help you gain an edge over the competition. We communicate clearly and quickly, build on flexible technologies, care about security and performance and build long-term partnerships based on trust and measurable results.',
    'about.paragraph4': 'We believe that technology should make people\'s work easier and open new opportunities. If you\'re looking for a reliable partner who will turn your idea into a functional custom-made tool and guide you through the entire process without unnecessary technical jargon, Next Layer Studio is the right choice – another layer of your success.',
    'about.team.ceo.name': 'Andrej Paulička',
    'about.team.ceo.position': 'Founder and CEO (Chief Executive Officer)\nHead of Design and Communication Department',
    'about.team.ceo.quote': 'Together we will always achieve the best solution for your business. I will make sure that we create the best design, work process and price offer that will suit you.',
    'about.team.dev.position': 'Head of Development Department',
    'about.team.dev.quote': 'Our technological solutions are built on modern technologies that ensure speed, security and scalability.',
    'about.team.marketing.position': 'Head of Marketing Department',
    'about.team.marketing.quote': 'Marketing is about stories and emotions. We help brands tell their story in a way that resonates with their audience.',
    'about.team.design.position': 'Head of Design Department',
    'about.team.design.quote': 'Design is the bridge between technology and user. We create interfaces that are not only beautiful, but also intuitive.',
    // Why Us page
    'whyUs.title': 'Why Choose Us',
    'whyUs.description': 'We are a young, flexible team that literally grew up on the internet; we don\'t follow trends from a distance, we live them every day. When developing websites and applications, we reach for the most modern technologies, but never at the expense of simplicity for you. From the first consultation to the final launch, we remain fast, open and ready to adapt exactly to what your brand needs.',
    'whyUs.conclusion': 'Young approach, latest technologies and absolute client orientation – that\'s Next Layer Studio. If you\'re looking for a partner who will transform your vision into a modern, powerful and perfectly personalized website or application, you\'re in the right place.',
    'whyUs.cards.ai.short': 'We use AI and our own processes to ensure your new modern website is completed with quality, speed and without stress.',
    'whyUs.cards.ai.long': 'We don\'t take artificial intelligence as a buzzword, but as a tool that speeds up analysis, helps generate design concepts and reveals bugs before they even get into production. Thanks to our own AI workflows, we shorten delivery time, reduce costs and guarantee consistent quality – without stress for you.',
    'whyUs.cards.modern.title': 'Modern Technologies',
    'whyUs.cards.modern.short': 'We are a generation that grew up on internet trends. What\'s "in" is not news to us, but a normal part of life.',
    'whyUs.cards.modern.long': 'React, Next.js, Tailwind, serverless cloud, CI/CD… these abbreviations are common language for us. We use them to make your website fast, secure and ready for future extensions. When a new technology appears, we immediately explore whether it can bring you a competitive advantage.',
    'whyUs.cards.personalization.short': 'Your website will be as unique as your brand – no templates, no clichés.',
    'whyUs.cards.personalization.long': 'No templates and "one-size-fits-all" solutions – every pixel and function is born from dialogue with you. We adapt design, content blocks and automated processes to your brand identity, so the result is as unique as you are.',
    'whyUs.cards.communication.short': 'We are open, accessible and happy to involve you in the whole process. Your opinion matters.',
    'whyUs.cards.communication.long': 'We believe that the best projects are born in discussion, not in silence. We continuously share prototypes, collect feedback and change direction according to what makes sense to you. You have direct contact with the developer and designer; your opinion is translated into code in real time.',
    'whyUs.cards.seo.short': 'Loading speed, semantic code, optimized images and technical settings of professional analytics ensure that Google not only sees you, but also moves you higher.',
    'whyUs.cards.seo.long': 'Loading speed, semantic code, optimized images and technical settings of professional analytics ensure that Google not only sees you, but also moves you higher. The result is more traffic without having to constantly pay for advertising.',
    'whyUs.cards.cms.short': 'We provide our own, intuitive editorial interface where you can change texts, images or add news without a single line of code.',
    'whyUs.cards.cms.long': 'We provide our own, intuitive editorial interface where you can change texts, images or add news without a single line of code. The less you depend on programmers for routine content management, the faster you can respond to market needs.',
    'whyUs.clickForMore': 'Click for more...',
    // Projects page
    'projects.title': 'Successful Projects',
    'projects.description1': 'Our portfolio is proof that quality work doesn\'t need big words. Every website, every page and every design we create carries our philosophy: personalization, speed, results.',
    'projects.description2': 'See how we helped brands grow, stand out from the crowd and engage their audience. Below you\'ll find a selection of our most successful projects.',
