    'modernization.heroSubtitle': 'Don\'t let an outdated website hold back your business growth. We modernize websites to be fast, secure, and conversion-focused.',
    'modernization.whyModernize.title': 'Why modernize your website?',
    'modernization.whyModernize.content': 'In today\'s digital age, your website is often the first point of contact for potential customers with your brand. If it\'s outdated or not functioning properly, you may miss out on important business opportunities. Modernization is not just about aesthetics – it\'s about a comprehensive improvement that delivers real results.',
